            <title>
                <![CDATA[上线一天后全面接管币安俄罗斯业务，横空出世的 CommEX 有何疑虑？]]>
            </title>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p class="intro_quote">币安于 27 日宣布全面退出俄罗斯市场，将业务出售给 CommEX，但币安与这家不知名交易所的关系也引起各界质疑。</p><p><strong>(回顾报导：<a href="https://abmedia.io/binance-exit-russia" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Binance 俄罗斯业务出售给 CommEX，完全退出俄罗斯市场</a>)</strong></p><div id="ez-toc-container" class="ez-toc-v2_0_55 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-grey ez-toc-container-direction"><div class="ez-toc-title-container"><p class="ez-toc-title ">内容目录</p><span class="ez-toc-title-toggle"><a href="https://abmedia.io/binance-sells-russian-unit-to-commex#" class="ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle" aria-label="Toggle Table of Content" role="button"><label for="item-65166fe334e42"><span class=""><span style="display:none;">Toggle</span><span class="ez-toc-icon-toggle-span"><svg style="fill: #999;color:#999"
